pymclust-native
=================

Native Python reimplementation of the R package mclust.

Goals
- Feature parity for Gaussian mixture modelling core: model-based clustering, classification, density estimation.
- Support for common covariance parameterizations from mclust (EII, VII, EEI, VEI, EVI, VVI, EEE, EVE, VEE, VVE, EVV, VVV).
- Model selection via BIC (and later ICL).

Status
- Early scaffold. APIs subject to change.

Development
- Python >= 3.9
- Dependencies: numpy, scipy
- Tests: pytest
